msgctxt "1016"
msgid "Jailhouse Snitch"
msgstr "Preso chismoso"

msgctxt "1020"
msgid "Saejima"
msgstr "Saejima"

msgctxt "84_Jailhouse Snitch"
msgid "So, what're you in for?"
msgstr "Eh... \\r\n"
"Oye... ¿Por qué estás aquí?"

msgctxt "96_Saejima"
msgid "Who, me?"
msgstr "... ¿Yo?"

msgctxt "108_Jailhouse Snitch"
msgid "You see anyone else around? Of course you! Must've done something big to end up in here. What was it? Arson? Assault? Grand theft auto?"
msgstr "Si llegaste a esta prisión, debes\\r\n"
"haber hecho algo bastante grave, ¿no?\\r\n"
"Cuéntame, ¿qué hiciste?"

msgctxt "120_Saejima"
msgid "I don't gotta tell ya a damn thing. Now back off 'fore I <Italic>make</Italic> you back off."
msgstr "No te diré nada.\\r\n"
"Deja de molestarme o <Italic>terminarás</Italic> herido."

msgctxt "132_Jailhouse Snitch"
msgid "Eep! Pretty sure I just pissed myself a little..."
msgstr "Je, je, je...\\r\n"
"D-da miedo, da miedo."

